Government (CCG). Ryan is a Green War rebel agent sent on a mission
 by Sponge (Danny Glover) to collect evidence against the CCG for its 
heinous crimes. Ryan soon faces the sinister Colonel Asimov, Major 
Anderson and a group of mercenaries lead by Lobo. Ryan's mission 
quickly turns chaotic when he meets Tuage, a mutant survivor of the 
CCG rebellion who swears to help Ryan save what is left of their world 
- or does she?
